{
  "texts": [
    "Two of these cases were due to the context size of the form being exceeded, rendering the GPT-4 model unable to produce meaningful outputs.",
    "In another case, the response generated by GPT-4 was nonsensical and could not be interpreted in a useful way.",
    "Similarly, Llama 2 was unable to produce viable responses in 14 out of 30 (46%) instances due to context size limitations.",
    "These limitations underscore the benefits of our approach.",
    "By constraining each LLM prompt to focus solely on one input and supplying contextualized information, FormNexus decreases the LLM's context size."
  ]
}